{"tid":1043636,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印度航母超日王號編隊出動 欲震懾基斯坦重鎮「喀拉蚩」","createTime":"2019-03-02T12:03:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-02T15:29:49.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ae2fce6a98f629e27b82b90bc3f7e0fb22a97884","tid":1043636,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T12:03:54.000Z","msg":"記者吳易達／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n印度目前唯一一艘可供部署的航母「維克拉瑪蒂亞號」（INS Vikramaditya）27日悄悄於孟買的印度海軍基地啟航，關閉了海上應答系統、去向不明。另外，一同出海的還有不少護衛艦艇與保障艦艇，陣容相當大。這次「維克拉瑪蒂亞號」的出動，被認為是印度至今最接近實戰的一次部署行動。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3930/3930280.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3930%2F3930280.jpg&h=55a3f2a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲▼印度航母「維克拉瑪蒂亞號」（INS Vikramaditya）,維克拉瑪蒂亞號,印度航母,INS Vikramaditya。（圖／維基百科）<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，印度此次派出航母的原因並不是要威懾巴基斯坦，而是為了避免印巴之間正面開戰而導致航母艦隊陷入被動；也有消息認為，這次「維克拉瑪蒂亞號」出海是為了在「關鍵位置」待命，防止局勢突然惡化，若印巴地區局勢持續惡化，「維克拉瑪蒂亞號」很有可能會對巴基斯坦軍事重鎮「喀拉蚩」進行空中打擊。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，此次印度派出的「維克拉瑪蒂亞號」是該國未來的海軍空兵主力，該艦排水量45,400噸，採常規動力推進，主力艦載機為俄製的米格-29K（MiG-29K）中型艦載機，能夠掛載R-73空對空導彈、S-24B火箭彈以及各類俄製導彈，總載彈量高達2.5噸。<br />\n<br />\n但由於該艦機庫大小有限，在正常情況下最多僅能搭載24架米格-29K戰鬥機，再加上沒有彈射裝置導致戰機出動效率較低，在單次投射的情況下威懾能力有限；用於壓制巴基斯坦地面目標效果則較為顯著。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文網址: 與巴空戰後 印度航母「維克拉瑪蒂亞號」出海搶占關鍵位置 | ETtoday軍武 | ETtoday新聞雲 <a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190302/1389779.htm#ixzz5h0zdcooX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190302%2F1389779.htm%23ixzz5h0zdcooX&d=Xug72IqGonTeMs94ciZuWv4FZ2Hvuo87ztF5QEQ%2B7nM%3D&h=899e6336\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190302/1389779.htm#ixzz5h0zdcooX</a>"},{"pid":"0b14dc21229410eb1eafec99815251368292f3bb","tid":1043636,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T12:40:10.000Z","msg":"有乜嘢飛機可以喺上面降落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5f40bb92ec932c63268326e34d3f74fad8041d8","tid":1043636,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T12:43:18.000Z","msg":"記者吳易達"},{"pid":"1ee2017d2c80ae3cd35fc7976336a6cd9f8f6f8f","tid":1043636,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T12:44:49.000Z","msg":"一睇就知同中國隻遼寧艦有得fight，勁呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ae4b5079eab93e2f5602a894cb6508f68693b4f","tid":1043636,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0b14dc21229410eb1eafec99815251368292f3bb","tid":1043636,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T12:40:10.000Z","msg":"有乜嘢飛機可以喺上面降落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T12:45:46.000Z","msg":"F35"},{"pid":"9ee2fb317fd91d78ed5a0004bb4891c0a93984f3","tid":1043636,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ae4b5079eab93e2f5602a894cb6508f68693b4f","tid":1043636,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0b14dc21229410eb1eafec99815251368292f3bb","tid":1043636,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T12:40:10.000Z","msg":"有乜嘢飛機可以喺上面降落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T12:45:46.000Z","msg":"F35"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T14:51:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n主力艦載機為俄製的米格-29K（MiG-29K）中型艦載機"},{"pid":"8f97ad8d78366b1597600b5333a77249b6aaf763","tid":1043636,"uid":11556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T15:29:49.000Z","msg":"印度最叻玩爛自己D玩具<br />\n希望呢隻航空母艦無事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}